definitions.definition: Midweek worship service, held by many congregations and in addition to a Sunday morning service.
examples: This Wednesday is churchwide midweek ; men's is the next one.
definitions.label_groups: Christianity , Latter-Day Saints , Jehovah's Witnesses , informal

secondary_definitions: ( Christianity , Latter-Day Saints , Jehovah's Witnesses , informal ) Midweek worship service, held by many congregations and in addition to a Sunday morning service.
